render_index(config, detected, profiles, stale_kickstarts)
detected_names = ", ".join(item.os_id for item in detected) if detected else "none"

Change it to this:

write_boot_ipxe(config, detected, profiles)
render_status(config, detected, profiles, stale_kickstarts)
